properties.name: Avon, North Carolina (The Outer Banks)
properties.description: Posted by EmichaudOuter Banks North CarolinaThe Outer Banks are located on an island off of the coast of North Carolina! My family always travels to the Outer Banks because there are a lot less tourists than other very well known beaches. Avon is the city we normally stay in and it is beautiful!

properties.name: Breckenridge, Colorado
properties.description: Posted by EmichaudColorado is one of the most beautiful places I have ever been to! Going to Colorado for vacation made me want to move there when I get older! I actually do not have any pictures with me from the trip so I uploaded this one from a website.

properties.name: Cesky Krumlov
properties.description: Posted by EmichaudaddressCesky Krumlov is located in the Czech Republic. Cesky Krumlov was a very cute town with beautiful scenery.

properties.name: Munich, Germany
properties.description: Posted by EmichaudMunich, GermanyMunich was an awesome place to go, but very crowded! There was so much to do in Munich, but not enough time! The first picture I attached is one of my friends and I with one of the lions they auction off on the sides of the street. The second picture I attached is from Hofbrauhaus. Hofbrauhaus is a very famous beer and food hall in Munich! Munich was a very cool place to visit!

properties.name: Orlando, FL
properties.description: Posted by EmichaudOrlando, FLDisney World has always been one of my favorite places to go on vacation!

properties.name: Philadelphia
properties.description: Posted by EmichaudPAI was actually born in Burlington, NJ (10 minutes outside of Philadelphia) so we visit the area a lot! I love going to Philadelphia, it seems like there is always something to do! The first picture I attached is of me and my sister tubing in Harrisburg, PA on my aunt\'s boat. The second picture was taken in Newark, NJ looking towards New York!

properties.name: Prague, Czech Republic
properties.description: Posted by EmichaudPrague was beautiful! Everything about Prague was gorgeous, we stayed in downtown Pragueand the last picture is actually a picture from our hotel room! Everything in Prague was amazing!

properties.name: Saint Thomas
properties.description: Posted by EmichaudSaint ThomasWhen my family went on a cruise, Saint Thomas was my favorite place we visited! The water was beautiful and the island was such a cool little place to stop at! Even though St. Thomas is very small, there is a lot to do! I really didn\'t take many pictures, but the first one is actually from on the cruise ship before we stopped at St. Thomas and the second is of the island.

properties.name: Salzburg
properties.description: Posted by EmichaudAustriaSalzburg was my favorite place in Europe I visited! We went to the Salt Mines which were very cool, you can actually taste salt on the rocks! The first picture is in the salt mines and the last picture I attached is me and three of my friends actually riding down one of the salt mines. The other three are pictures of the city of Salzburg which was the most beautiful place I have ever seen!

properties.name: Vienna, Austria
properties.description: Posted by EmichaudVienna, AustriaOn my senior trip, I went to Europe! Vienna was one of the cities we visited! Vienna was beautiful!!
